<h2>Berakhyah Ben Natronai ha-Nakdan, Sefer Ko'ah ha-Avanim / On the Virtue of the Stones (Monographie)</h2>
<h3>Hebrew Text and English Translation. With a Lexicological Analysis of the Romance Terminology and Source Study</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='358'></abbr>
